|footnotes              = * Stavelot to {{flagicon|Dutch Republic}} [[United Kingdom of the Netherlands]]; [[Malmedy]] to {{flag|Prussia|1803|name=Prussian}} province of [[Province of J<U+00FC>lich-Cleves-Berg|J<U+00FC>lich-Cleves-Berg]]
